headline: Fastenal (FAST): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Fastenal has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 3.5% while holding steady at $40.19. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 13.1% gain during that period.
